long_description: from formal and elegant to fresh, fun or rustic designs, the sign me up team create commercial art and signage for a wide variety of applications. if you're looking for a professional vancouver sign shop, you've come to the right place. we specialize in large scale sign painting and large format printing plus enjoy creating many other custom signage requests like 3d cut signs, window display, sandwich boards, wood signs, boutique signs for retail & more. a few years after high school i decided to go to 'sign school' where we not only learned on computers but the old school way of hand painted letters. we're located in beautiful vancouver, bc, near olympic village. we're excited to hear your vision and provide viable solutions that will truly make a difference for your business or organization.
